<!-- About Section -->
<section class="bg-surface-container-low py-32 px-12" id="about">
<div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-24">
<div class="md:col-span-7">
<p class="text-label text-primary mb-6">About the practice</p>
<h2 class="text-4xl font-headline italic mb-8">Guided by empathy, grounded in science.</h2>
<div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-on-surface-variant font-light leading-relaxed">
<p>In our sessions, we move beyond just managing symptoms. We create a dialogue—a quiet, intentional space where we can explore the layers of your experience with curiosity rather than judgment.</p>
<p>My approach is rooted in Scandinavian principles of professional warmth and functional minimalism. I believe therapy should feel like a sanctuary—a room where you can set down the weight of expectations and begin to speak your truth into existence.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-5 flex flex-col justify-center">
<div class="border-l-[0.5px] border-tertiary-container pl-12 space-y-12 py-4">
<div>
<p class="text-label mb-2">Education</p>
<p class="font-headline italic text-xl">Ph.D. in Clinical Psychology</p>
<p class="text-sm font-light text-on-surface-variant">University of Copenhagen</p>
</div>
<div>
<p class="text-label mb-2">Philosophy</p>
<p class="font-headline italic text-xl">Humanistic-Existential Approach</p>
<p class="text-sm font-light text-on-surface-variant">CBT &amp; Mindfulness Integration</p>
</div>
<div>
<p class="text-label mb-2">Accreditation</p>
<p class="font-headline italic text-xl">Licensed Psychotherapist</p>
<p class="text-sm font-light text-on-surface-variant">Member of the BPS &amp; APA</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
