<!-- FAQ Section -->
<section class="py-32 px-12 max-w-screen-md mx-auto" id="faq">
<div class="text-center mb-20">
<p class="text-label text-primary mb-4">Common Questions</p>
<h2 class="text-4xl font-headline italic">Seeking clarity.</h2>
</div>
<div class="space-y-4">
<!-- Accordion Style Item -->
<details class="group p-6 border-b border-tertiary-container/30 open:bg-surface-container-low transition-all rounded-xl">
<summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex justify-between items-center text-on-surface font-light text-lg">
<span>How long does a session last?</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary-container group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="mt-6 text-on-surface-variant font-light leading-relaxed">
                        Standard sessions are 50 minutes long. This allows for a focused dialogue while leaving time for transition and reflection.
                    </div>
</details>
<details class="group p-6 border-b border-tertiary-container/30 open:bg-surface-container-low transition-all rounded-xl">
<summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex justify-between items-center text-on-surface font-light text-lg">
<span>Do you offer online consultations?</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary-container group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="mt-6 text-on-surface-variant font-light leading-relaxed">
                        Yes, I offer secure video consultations for clients who are unable to visit the office in person. The quality of care remains our primary focus.
                    </div>
</details>
<details class="group p-6 border-b border-tertiary-container/30 open:bg-surface-container-low transition-all rounded-xl">
<summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex justify-between items-center text-on-surface font-light text-lg">
<span>Is my privacy protected?</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary-container group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="mt-6 text-on-surface-variant font-light leading-relaxed">
                        Confidentiality is the cornerstone of our practice. All records are stored according to GDPR and professional ethical standards.
                    </div>
</details>
<details class="group p-6 border-b border-tertiary-container/30 open:bg-surface-container-low transition-all rounded-xl">
<summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex justify-between items-center text-on-surface font-light text-lg">
<span>What is your cancellation policy?</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary-container group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="mt-6 text-on-surface-variant font-light leading-relaxed">
                        I ask for at least 24 hours' notice for cancellations. This allows me to offer the time to another person who may be waiting for support.
                    </div>
</details>
<details class="group p-6 border-b border-tertiary-container/30 open:bg-surface-container-low transition-all rounded-xl">
<summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex justify-between items-center text-on-surface font-light text-lg">
<span>How many sessions will I need?</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary-container group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="mt-6 text-on-surface-variant font-light leading-relaxed">
                        The duration of therapy is highly individual. Some find clarity in a few sessions, while others benefit from longer-term exploratory work.
                    </div>
</details>
<details class="group p-6 border-b border-tertiary-container/30 open:bg-surface-container-low transition-all rounded-xl">
<summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex justify-between items-center text-on-surface font-light text-lg">
<span>Do you accept insurance?</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary-container group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="mt-6 text-on-surface-variant font-light leading-relaxed">
                        I work with several major providers. Please contact me with your details so we can verify coverage before our first session.
